Come hang out with me at the SOCALTECH Fair! https://ibp.gg/SoCalTechFair

Is GameStop's Retro program as bad as people (like me) say? I traded in my old consoles and bought six different retro systems to find out...with some VERY surprising results. Some consoles were disgusting, but others were actually kind of worth it?
